723161f-a.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Avenue - 190th Street
723161f-a.text:
1591 St. Nicholas Avenue (formerly Eleventh Avenue) at N.W. corner
of 190th Street. The view is west on the north side of 190th
Street. This is one of the early apartment houses of the Fort
George section; it was built around 1V14.
October 26, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
